Think of it Like This 🎯
Real LifeGit BranchesPhotocopy a documentCreate a branchEdit the photocopyMake changes in branchCompare with originalPull Request reviewReplace original if goodMerge to main

Key Points ✅

Branch = exact copy of main at that point in time
You only add or edit what you need
Original main stays untouched until merge
No need to recreate existing files ever! 🚀
